	to you app's appinfo.json.<br>
	When the system laucnhes your app in exhibition it passes the parameter <b><i>touchstoneMode=true</b></i> 
	to the app-assistant's handleLaunch.<br />
	When this app is selected it launches a screen save type sceen.
